content:
I have ongoing interests in human rights, humanitarian practice, and medicine. Currently, I am the co-chair of the Physicians for Human Rights Student Advisory Board. I have also worked with the Philadelphia Human Rights Clinic, Doctors 4 Camp Closure, and Doctors for America on projects related to human rights.
I have written on topics in human rights as a member of the advocacy committee on the student advisory board for Physicians for Human Rights. You can see some of that work here and here.
Back to my work&hellip;
